				<a href="http://www.bristoliww.org.uk/last-branch-meeting-of-2016-and-social/" rel="bookmark">
					Last Branch Meeting of 2016 and SOCIAL!				</a>
			</h3>
			<div class="mh-meta mh-loop-meta">
				<span class="mh-meta-date updated"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>Thursday December  1st, 2016</span>
<span class="mh-meta-author author vcard"><i class="fa fa-user"></i><a class="fn" href="http://www.bristoliww.org.uk/author/pasionaria/">Bristol Comms Officer</a></span>
<span class="mh-meta-comments"><i class="fa fa-comment-o"></i><a class="mh-comment-count-link" href="http://www.bristoliww.org.uk/last-branch-meeting-of-2016-and-social/#mh-comments">0</a></span>
			</div>
		</header>
		<div class="mh-loop-excerpt">
			<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>With 2016 coming to an end Bristol IWW are having their last branch meeting on: Friday 9th December at Hydra Books from 7.30 &#8211; 8pm. <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="http://www.bristoliww.org.uk/last-branch-meeting-of-2016-and-social/" title="Last Branch Meeting of 2016 and SOCIAL!">[&#8230;]</a></p>
